description: Reconcile cells in column NAME to type http://www.geonames.org/ontology#Feature
Create column name at index 1 based on column NAME using expression grel:cell.recon.match.id
Create column NAME_URI at index 1 based on column NAME using expression grel:value.replace(" ","").replace(" - ", "")
Text transform on cells in column NAME_URI using expression grel:value.replace(".","").replace("'","").replace("-","")
Text transform on cells in column NAME_URI using expression grel:value.replace("(","").replace(",","").replace(")","")
